# Title: Arbitrary File Download Via MSEDGE_PROXY.EXE
# Author: Swachchhanda Shrawan Poudel
# Date: 2023-11-09
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects usage of "msedge_proxy.exe" to download arbitrary files
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1218
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_msedge_proxy_download.yml

CommandLine IN ("*http://*", "*https://*") Image="*\\msedge_proxy.exe" OR OriginalFileName="msedge_proxy.exe"